    "title": {
      "rendered": "Ten Must-Follow Nonprofits on LinkedIn"
    },
    "content": {
      "rendered": "<p><a href=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/10-Must-Follow-Nonprofits-o.jpg\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignright size-medium wp-image-13982\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" alt=\"10-Must-Follow-Nonprofits-o\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/10-Must-Follow-Nonprofits-o-300x300.jpg?resize=300%2C300\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/10-Must-Follow-Nonprofits-o.jpg?resize=300%2C300&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/10-Must-Follow-Nonprofits-o.jpg?resize=150%2C150&amp;ssl=1 150w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/10-Must-Follow-Nonprofits-o.jpg?resize=200%2C200&amp;ssl=1 200w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/10-Must-Follow-Nonprofits-o.jpg?resize=75%2C75&amp;ssl=1 75w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/10-Must-Follow-Nonprofits-o.jpg?w=500&amp;ssl=1 500w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" /></a>Some nonprofits have thousands, tens of thousands, even hundreds of thousands of <a href=\"http://www.linkedin.com/company/509171\">LinkedIn Company Page</a> followers, and yet have not customized their page or posted a single update. LinkedIn Pages launched in 2010 and since then the company has <em>slowly</em> rolled out upgrades and new features. So slow in fact that LinkedIn Pages have fallen under the radar of most nonprofits, but in recent months interest and engagement on LinkedIn Pages has been steadily growing and some nonprofits are beginning to take notice and adding LinkedIn Pages to their priority lists and editorial calendars.</p>\n<p>If your nonprofit decides to become active on LinkedIn, it&#8217;s recommended that you follow some of the early adopters and study their LinkedIn Pages to help get a sense of the LinkedIn community and what type of content they engage with. That said, it&#8217;s a recurring trend and worth noting that nonprofits who work on environmental issues and international development tend to be the early adopters of most new social networking tools. I browsed the LinkedIn Pages of over 200 of the most well-known nonprofits in the world and the following ten are clearly taking the lead:</p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">1. American Red Cross<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.linkedin.com/company/american-red-cross\">linkedin.com/company/american-red-cross</a></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/American-Red-Cross.png\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-13961\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" alt=\"American Red Cross\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/American-Red-Cross.png?resize=600%2C279\" width=\"600\" height=\"279\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/American-Red-Cross.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/American-Red-Cross.png?resize=300%2C139&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">2. Ashoka<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.linkedin.com/company/ashoka\">linkedin.com/company/ashoka</a></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/Ashoka.png\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-13963\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" alt=\"Ashoka\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/Ashoka.png?resize=600%2C279\" width=\"600\" height=\"279\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/Ashoka.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/Ashoka.png?resize=300%2C139&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">3. Conservation International<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.linkedin.com/company/conservation-international\">linkedin.com/company/conservation-international</a></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/Conservation-International.png\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-13965\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" alt=\"Conservation International\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/Conservation-International.png?resize=600%2C279\" width=\"600\" height=\"279\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/Conservation-International.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/Conservation-International.png?resize=300%2C139&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">4. Environmental Defense Fund<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.linkedin.com/company/environmental-defense\">linkedin.com/company/environmental-defense</a></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/Environmental-Defense-Fund.png\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-13968\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" alt=\"Environmental Defense Fund\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/Environmental-Defense-Fund.png?resize=600%2C279\" width=\"600\" height=\"279\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/Environmental-Defense-Fund.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/Environmental-Defense-Fund.png?resize=300%2C139&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong style=\"font-size: 1.5em;\">5. Nature Conservancy of Canada<br />\n<strong><a href=\"http://www.linkedin.com/company/127032\">linkedin.com/company/nature-conservancy-of-canada</a></strong></strong><strong><br />\n</strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/Nature-Conservancy-of-Canda.png\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-13970\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" alt=\"Nature Conservancy of Canda\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/Nature-Conservancy-of-Canda.png?resize=600%2C279\" width=\"600\" height=\"279\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/Nature-Conservancy-of-Canda.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/Nature-Conservancy-of-Canda.png?resize=300%2C139&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">6. National Wildlife Federation<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.linkedin.com/company/11401\">linkedin.com/company/national-wildlife-federation</a></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/Nature-Wildlife-Federation.png\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-13971\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" alt=\"Nature Wildlife Federation\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/Nature-Wildlife-Federation.png?resize=600%2C279\" width=\"600\" height=\"279\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/Nature-Wildlife-Federation.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/Nature-Wildlife-Federation.png?resize=300%2C139&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">7. PATH<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.linkedin.com/company/9100\">linkedin.com/company/path</a></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/PATH.png\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-13973\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" alt=\"PATH\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/PATH.png?resize=600%2C279\" width=\"600\" height=\"279\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/PATH.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/PATH.png?resize=300%2C139&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">8. Plan International<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.linkedin.com/company/10753\">linkedin.com/company/plan-international</a></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/Plan-International.png\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-13974\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" alt=\"Plan International\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/Plan-International.png?resize=600%2C279\" width=\"600\" height=\"279\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/Plan-International.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/Plan-International.png?resize=300%2C139&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">9. Public Broadcasting Service (PBS)<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.linkedin.com/company/public-broadcasting-service\">linkedin.com/company/public-broadcasting-service</a></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/PBS.png\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-13976\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" alt=\"PBS\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/PBS.png?resize=600%2C279\" width=\"600\" height=\"279\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/PBS.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/PBS.png?resize=300%2C139&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">10. United Nations Development Programme<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.linkedin.com/company/undp/\">linkedin.com/company/undp</a></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/UNDP.png\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-13977\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" alt=\"UNDP\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/UNDP.png?resize=600%2C279\" width=\"600\" height=\"279\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/UNDP.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/UNDP.png?resize=300%2C139&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Over the next couple of months Nonprofit Tech for Good will be posting LinkedIn Page tips and resources. To learn how to better utilize LinkedIn Pages, please follow the Nonprofit Tech for Good LinkedIn Page:</p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Nonprofit Tech for Good<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.linkedin.com/company/509171\">linkedin.com/company/nonprofit-tech-for-good</a></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/NPTECHforGOOD.png\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-13979\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" alt=\"NPTECHforGOOD\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/NPTECHforGOOD.png?resize=600%2C279\" width=\"600\" height=\"279\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/NPTECHforGOOD.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/NPTECHforGOOD.png?resize=300%2C139&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n",
